<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="yes" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="nominative">which itself</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 is the third largest city in Australia, with a population of just under 2.0 million and an urban agglomeration of over 2.4 million people. 
